# 止蝕
(pos:動詞)
<explanation>
yue:喺投資、買賣等活動入面，阻止虧損，令損失唔再繼續增加。
eng:to stop losses (in investment or trading)
<eg>
yue:個股價跌到咁低，我決定止蝕，唔好再蝕咁多啦。 (go3 gu2 gaa3 dit3 dou3 gam3 dai1, ngo5 gok3 ding3 zi2 sit1, m4 hou2 zoi3 sit1 gam3 do1 laa1.)
eng:The stock price has dropped so low, I've decided to cut my losses and not lose any more. [end of text]


